OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FPotholes have become a major problem
OL,7,Facross the South, with 1,300 defects
OL,8,Freported in a single week in
OL,9,FOxfordshire.
OL,11,FWith more extreme weather patterns
OL,12,Fit's not an issue that's likely to go
OL,13,Faway, so to try and fix it, highway
OL,14,Fcrews have been trialling new and
OL,15,Fexisting pothole repair equipment and
OL,16,Ftechnology on a stretch of road in
OL,17,FBanbury.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
