FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FAfter a winter that saw a dramatic
OL,7,Frise in the number of potholes
OL,8,Freported nationally and locally, a
OL,9,Ftrial has taken place aimed at
OL,10,Fimproving the repair process in
OL,11,FOxfordshire for the future.
OL,13,FOxfordshire County Council and its
OL,14,Fhighways contractor M Group used
OL,15,FWildmere Road in Banbury as a test
OL,16,Fsite to trial 15 different methods of
OL,17,Ffilling in potholes or 'patching'
OL,18,Fminor defects.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FSome of these methods are already used
OL,7,Fin Oxfordshire, while the others were
OL,8,Fnew technology sourced by M Group.
OL,10,FWildmere Road was closed and a 700-
OL,11,Fmetre stretch was divided into
OL,12,Fsections. Each section had a different
OL,13,Ftype of pothole or patch repair
OL,14,Fcarried out to get a direct comparison
OL,15,Fof the various methods.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FIt is the second time the council has
OL,7,Fcarried out a pothole repair
OL,8,Finnovation event, following a similar
OL,9,Ftrial in Steventon in 2023, believed
OL,10,Fto have been the first of its kind in
OL,11,Fthe country.
OL,13,FSeven repair methods were trialled in
OL,14,F2023, making this week's event a much
OL,15,Flarger undertaking.
OL,17,FThe cost of bringing pothole-plagued
OL,18,Flocal roads in England and Wales up to
OL,19,Fscratch has been estimated to be a
OL,20,Frecord #18.6 billion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FCouncillor Liz Leffman, Oxfordshire
OL,7,FCounty Council's Cabinet Member for
OL,8,FHighways Construction and Repair,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The impact of potholes on our
OL,10,Froads this winter, not just in
OL,11,FOxfordshire but nationwide, has been
OL,12,Funprecedented.
OL,14,F"We are committed to seeking new and
OL,15,Finnovative methods of carrying out
OL,16,Frepairs on our 3,000 mile road
OL,17,Fnetwork. Technology is changing all
OL,18,Fthe time and it is important to test
OL,19,Fthe latest products to maximise value
OL,20,Ffor money when it comes to highway
OL,21,Fmaintenance.
OL,26,@qD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,F"The 2023 event led to us adopting
OL,7,Fseveral new methods of repair, and
OL,8,Fruling out others, so we hope this
OL,9,Flatest trial will provide evidence and
OL,10,Finformation for our contractors about
OL,11,Fwhat repair methods work best by
OL,12,Ftesting them on the same stretch of
OL,13,Froad."
OL,15,FSince January 2026, M Group has
OL,16,Frepaired more than 33,000 highways
OL,17,Fdefects ` compared to 37,042 potholes
OL,18,Ffilled in the whole of the 2024 - 25.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FThis was against a backdrop of perfect
OL,7,Fpothole-forming weather conditions
OL,8,Fthis winter ` a prolonged freeze
OL,9,Ffollowed by a protracted period of
OL,10,Frain, which led to an unprecedented
OL,11,Fincrease in the number of emergency
OL,12,Fpothole reports.
OL,14,FThe council was receiving more than
OL,15,F1,000 reports a week, reaching over
OL,16,F1,300 defects in a single week in
OL,17,Fearly March.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FAs a result, the number of repair
OL,7,Fcrews was increased from seven to 25
OL,8,Fto reduce a backlog of potholes caused
OL,9,Fby the weather.
OL,11,FRichard Lovewell, M Group Business
OL,12,FDirector, said: "From introducing the
OL,13,FDragon Patcher back in 2015 to hosting
OL,14,Fthe UK's first pothole trial day in
OL,15,F2023, M Group and Oxfordshire County
OL,16,FCouncil have a strong track record of
OL,17,Fworking together to find better ways
OL,18,Fto maintain and repair roads.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,F"This latest trial is about building
OL,7,Fon that progress. By testing new
OL,8,Fproducts and approaches we can ensure
OL,9,Fthat we are using the best value
OL,10,Fmaterials in the right conditions and
OL,11,Fthe right places, increasing
OL,12,Fefficiency and durability, and
OL,13,Fdelivering better value for
OL,14,FOxfordshire residents.
OL,16,F"With wetter winters and hotter
OL,17,Fsummers, it is vital we keep adapting
OL,18,Four maintenance techniques to cope
OL,19,Fwith increasing pressure on our road
OL,20,Fnetworks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781784675
OL,3,CFifteen ways to solve the pothole
OL,4,Cproblem
OL,6,FWildmere Road will be monitored
OL,7,Fregularly over the next two years to
OL,8,Fallow comparisons of the type of
OL,9,Frepair, equipment, material, and
OL,10,Flabour used, and the time taken.
OL,12,FThis will include an understanding of
OL,13,Fthe potential results, longevity of
OL,14,Frepairs, waste generated, carbon
OL,15,Fimpact, use of recycled content and
OL,16,Fproductivity that may be achievable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/10
